cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.Medical Imaging, cs.NE 

The paper deals with medical image segmentation using deep learning and data augmentation techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the effectiveness of deep learning models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The focus on medical imaging tasks makes cs.Medical Imaging a likely category. Finally, the use of deep learning models and data augmentation techniques suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
